n></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">1,000</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">year investment horizon</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">427 CE</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">Nalanda founded</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">1,500</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">years of proof</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">700</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">years Nalanda lasted</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">9M</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">manuscripts in the Dharmaganja</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">10,000</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">students at peak</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">1,000</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">year investment horizon</span></div><div class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__item\"><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__number\">427 CE</span><span class=\"ImpactBar-module__UgDHrq__label\">Nalanda founded</span></div></div></div><section class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__section SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__cream \"><div class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__inner \"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__header SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__left\"><span class=\"EyebrowLabel-module__gRM9Oq__eyebrowLabel \">Ventures</span><h2 class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__headline SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\"><span>Founders we are<br/></span><span>honored to stand beside.</span></h2><p class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__subhead SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\">A small sample of the work already underway. Each venture is a long-term relationship, not a single transaction.</p></div><div class=\"grid-3\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><a class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__card\" href=\"/portfolio/c-link\"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__header\"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__tags\"><span class=\"Tag-module__SiXDDq__tag Tag-module__SiXDDq__gold\">Circular Economy</span></div><h3 class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__name\">C-link</h3></div><p class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__description\">What C-Link Does\n\nC-Link transforms organic waste streams into verified carbon removal and agricultural products through Terrestrial Storage. Our facilities process municipal biosolids, green waste, agricultural residues, and disaster debris—materials that traditionally create methane emissions, fire hazards, and disposal costs—and convert them into stable carbon storage and regenerative soil inputs.\n</p></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__section SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__white \"><div class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__inner \"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__header SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__left\"><span class=\"EyebrowLabel-module__gRM9Oq__eyebrowLabel \">The collective</span><h2 class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__headline SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\"><span>The people carrying<br/></span><span>this work forward.</span></h2><p class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__subhead SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\">Operators, scientists, and stewards who have spent years building in the real world — now in service to founders.</p></div><div class=\"grid-3\"><div><a href=\"/team/benjamin-callis\" class=\"block bg-white border border-[color:var(--color-border-light)] p-4 no-underline hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)] transition-all duration-300\"><p class=\"text-[color:var(--color-text-tertiary)] text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1\">Founder</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl italic text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-1\">Benjamin Callis</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)]\">Founder</p></a></div><div><a href=\"/team/cj\" class=\"block bg-white border border-[color:var(--color-border-light)] p-4 no-underline hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)] transition-all duration-300\"><p class=\"text-[color:var(--color-text-tertiary)] text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1\">Founder</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl italic text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-1\">Christopher Johnson</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)]\">Founder</p></a></div><div><a href=\"/team/lorraine\" class=\"block bg-white border border-[color:var(--color-border-light)] p-4 no-underline hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)] transition-all duration-300\"><p class=\"text-[color:var(--color-text-tertiary)] text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-1\">Advisor</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl italic text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-1\">Lorraine Bassett MBA, PHD</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)]\">Impact Advisor</p></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__section SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__cream \"><div class=\"SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__inner SectionWrapper-module__TaJyhW__narrow\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__header SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__left\"><span class=\"EyebrowLabel-module__gRM9Oq__eyebrowLabel \">Journal</span><h2 class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__headline SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\"><span>Thinking in<br/></span><span>longer timescales.</span></h2><p class=\"SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__subhead SectionHeader-module__nw_e0a__light\">Selected essays and dispatches from the work — reflections on power, coherence, and what it means to build for a future that will remember us.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><a href=\"/blog/risk-return-impact\" class=\"block border-t border-[color:var(--color-border-light)] py-4 no-underline group\"><p class=\"text-[color:var(--color-text-tertiary)] text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-2\">Feb 18, 2026</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl italic text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-1 group-hover:text-[color:var(--color-gold)] transition-colors\">Risk-Return-Impact</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)]\">The Risk-Return-Impact (RRI) model emerged from a simple observation: the businesses generating the highest returns in our portfolio were also creating the most measurable positive change. Not sometimes. Consistently.</p></a><a href=\"/blog/the-shift-from-stem-cells-to-signals\" class=\"block border-t border-[color:var(--color-border-light)] py-4 no-underline group\"><p class=\"text-[color:var(--color-text-tertiary)] text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-2\">Jan 3, 2026</p><h3 class=\"font-serif text-xl italic text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-1 group-hover:text-[color:var(--color-gold)] transition-colors\">The Shift from Stem Cells to Signals</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)]\">The Shift from Stem Cells to Signals: A New Era of Longevity\nFor decades, we believed the secret to longevity lay in replacing our cells like worn-out parts in a machine. \n</p></a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div><footer class=\"bg-[#0F1A14] text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-serif text-xl mb-4\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#52B788] text-[#0F1A14] te